=== Test 1: Agnostic set then unset ===
After set:
  MemoAgnostic exists: true
  MemoAgnostic get: int(42)
  MemoSensitive exists: false
  MemoSensitive get: NULL
After unset:
  MemoAgnostic exists: false
  MemoAgnostic get: NULL
  MemoSensitive exists: false
  MemoSensitive get: NULL
After unset scope:
  MemoAgnostic exists: true
  MemoAgnostic get: int(42)
  MemoSensitive exists: false
  MemoSensitive get: NULL
=== Test 2: Sensitive set then unset ===
After set:
  MemoAgnostic exists: false
  MemoAgnostic get: NULL
  MemoSensitive exists: true
  MemoSensitive get: int(99)
After unset:
  MemoAgnostic exists: false
  MemoAgnostic get: NULL
  MemoSensitive exists: false
  MemoSensitive get: NULL
After unset scope:
  MemoAgnostic exists: false
  MemoAgnostic get: NULL
  MemoSensitive exists: true
  MemoSensitive get: int(99)
=== Test 3: Set both, unset agnostic only ===
Both set:
  MemoAgnostic exists: true
  MemoAgnostic get: int(10)
  MemoSensitive exists: true
  MemoSensitive get: int(20)
Agnostic unset, sensitive remains:
  MemoAgnostic exists: false
  MemoAgnostic get: NULL
  MemoSensitive exists: true
  MemoSensitive get: int(20)
=== Test 4: Set both, unset sensitive only ===
Both set:
  MemoAgnostic exists: true
  MemoAgnostic get: int(10)
  MemoSensitive exists: true
  MemoSensitive get: int(20)
Sensitive unset, agnostic remains:
  MemoAgnostic exists: true
  MemoAgnostic get: int(10)
  MemoSensitive exists: false
  MemoSensitive get: NULL
=== Test 5: Unset without prior set ===
Agnostic unset (was never set):
  MemoAgnostic exists: false
  MemoAgnostic get: NULL
  MemoSensitive exists: false
  MemoSensitive get: NULL
Sensitive unset (was never set):
  MemoAgnostic exists: false
  MemoAgnostic get: NULL
  MemoSensitive exists: false
  MemoSensitive get: NULL
